</title>
<subSubSection id="8D0C79F960B560382AC04E8D343BF249" pageId="null" pageNumber="183" type="description">
<paragraph id="3A2B0CE1C2EA142614F0430FEF0675EF" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
Ausdauernd mit Pfahlwurzel und kurzem, verzweigtem Rhizom; 20 
<emphasis id="5A00E4B61EF2FA5DADEBFA86A49C2EB5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
60 cm hoch. Stengel aufrecht, kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="E9F1366E04316FF77A41E1B84FA3BA60" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="E510CCF8EFC428DC4CD6394C45A0BF92" originalValue="grundständiger" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">grundstaendiger</normalizedToken>
Rosette und am Stengel, gestielt, kahl, 
<emphasis id="3B31003564468BA91767521BA6093AB8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">ungeteilt und ganzrandig bis wenig tief und</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="85D425BF4D35A2672C8931F588ECDD1C" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">+/-</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="5017FA49C03A7EC8B0FEEBD4A91555F3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
stumpf 
<normalizedToken id="8210BCD07BC754E9296194BA26B4C571" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
, oval.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="633AF6F137C53BB5E877E4C9C8F5CA3E" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
⅔-1mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="B2E73807FA57766AA1A4424AD61091D8" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="88DA5B0427D666F08A662AAD32BF14B8" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
aufrecht, 6 
<emphasis id="0B744907F299CCEF44C1ABC2FB1E2F4B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
10 mm lang, kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="8C1F8D342432C1DA4401E5AA30639909" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
lang gestielt, 12 
<emphasis id="45E17856F71FF6617C4A5C4667FCD34C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
18 mm lang, gelb; Stiel 2mal so lang wie der 
<normalizedToken id="CD440538DD2C11FCF4CD3528A1EE09AD" originalValue="übrige" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">uebrige</normalizedToken>
(breite) Teil des Kronblattes; Fruchtstiele 8 
<emphasis id="3BEF28DA9BFAB97B439F5D3D8D9585F7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
15 mm lang. 
<normalizedToken id="45B7BBDB1E6EADDA118AF7C38D1DCA10" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="AFEDB4BCB6F1A8B983536637B9429A59" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">+/-</normalizedToken>
waagrecht abstehend, 4,5 
<emphasis id="1733FCED53D6183FCD4DAF5B004C4367" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
8 cm lang und 
<emphasis id="8B2CC4AA5443A049453A09703C3E2E12" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">2,5-3 mm dick, kahl;</emphasis>
Schnabel 8 
<emphasis id="4AC2DC20416B5319FDC9D24EC5B4654D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
22 mm lang, mit 1 
<emphasis id="D6DD427FAD09E80656354DFB99EF092F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
4 Samen. Samen 1 
<emphasis id="A4C1CDBCDB5ED2CBEFD71AD5A3FCCB28" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
1,5 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="F4718855AC2102722AAE68901A037753" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B2CF24436B273B10A12AA58029213F4F" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="DA59ACF2CEB571B51AC783FE5B60F31E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="78B073F06EB44E5B143AEFDE3CB094F1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">24:</emphasis>
Material aus den Westalpen (Delay 1968, Favarger 1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5A500E9E6D4FFBA34B41CA42C4ECBCDA" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="612B1D24DEA5B8BCB3600844F65711CA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Kiesige bis felsige, kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="B6077D5FBA8B35BFD80F1F40F120B56A" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="57D27EA9C8A99F4CF82B7FB875C6E091" originalValue="Geröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Geroell</normalizedToken>
, Felsschutt, Felsspalten, Alluvionen, steinige Weiden.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="074EA58F0451624C15A93E20717C1681" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="30C790E96AE41D16CBE6EF03B8E5452D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Verbreitung. Westalpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
Monte Viso bis Mont Cenis. - Im Gebiet: Maurienne (Valmeinier, Gegend des Mont Cenis).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
